description: Trip`s Timburr evolved sometime between its battle with Ash`s Oshawott and its reveal at the Don George tournament in Raimon Town. Trip`s Gurdurr battled against Cilan`s Dwebble in the first round of the Don George tournament. It ended up loosing to Cilan`s Dwebble after it got stuck under a rock from Rock Slide.
name: Dotekkotsu (Shootie)
